{"id":"naarah","term":"Naarah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A girl, the second of Ashur’s two wives, of the tribe of Judah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 4:5\">1 Chr. 4:5</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 4:6\">6</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 4:5","1 Chronicles 4:6"]}